# Visual Design Proposal for Horace Englossed Interactive Digital Edition

## Introduction
This document outlines a concrete design proposal for the Horace Englossed interactive digital edition, focusing on the visual aspects of the project.

## Color Scheme
- **Primary Color**: Soft Blue (#A7C6ED)
- **Secondary Color**: Warm Beige (#F0E6D2)
- **Accent Color**: Deep Charcoal (#333333)
- **Text Color**: Dark Gray (#4A4A4A)
- **Background Color**: White (#FFFFFF)

## Layout Sketches
- **Homepage**: A clean design with sections for featured content and navigation links to interactive elements.
- **Content Pages**: A two-column layout where the primary text appears on the left and interactive content (like footnotes and illustrations) appears on the right.
- **Footer**: Contains links to social media, copyright information, and navigation links.

