## Typography
- **Headings**: 'Playfair Display', Serif 36px, Bold
- **Body Text**: 'Roboto', Sans-serif 16px, Regular
- **Links**: 'Roboto', Sans-serif 16px, Italic (Primary color)

## Design Decisions
- **Accessibility**: Color contrast ratios will be ensured to meet WCAG standards, providing readability for all users.
- **Interactivity**: Subtle animations will be used to enhance user engagement without distracting from the content.
- **Responsiveness**: The layout will be designed to be fully responsive, ensuring good usability on both mobile and desktop devices.

## Conclusion
This visual design proposal aims to create a cohesive and engaging experience for users of the Horace Englossed interactive digital edition, marrying aesthetics with functionality to enhance user experience.
